org.fiware.cybercaptor.server.remediation.cost

Class OperationalCostParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fiware.cybercaptor.server.remediation.cost.OperationalCostParameters

  • public class OperationalCostParameters
extends Object
    Class that represents the remediation operational cost parameters (direct cost to deploy the deployable remediation) there is a global OperationalCostsParameters for each remediation type, but it can also be customised for each remediation
    Author:
    Francois -Xavier Aguessy
